OFFSETLESS INJECTOR by devkanel
yo, i made this injector so u dont have to deal with annoying offsets every time the game updates.

how it works:
it uses thread hijacking and module stomps your dll into d3d10warps.dll. simple as that.

there’s a driver included in the files but the injector doesn't use it by default, but it's there if u want to set it up yourself to stay fully undetected.

NOTE: if the project wont build, it’s probably cuz u don't got the WDK (windows driver kit) installed. just unload the driver project and it should build.

also, thejre is a small flaw,
I've added TLS and SEH (creds to cherpixel for seh and tls) but i still heard with some big dlls it might crash, u can try stomping mshtml.dll if u need more space but the injector is stable,
but if you experience crashes when injecting, its the injector, it injects but some dlls fail, you can fork the repo and try fixing that, if u do fix it, dm me on discord (@kaneldev) and ill 
accept the merge. but that's pretty much it, i currently also have

contact / help
if it still wont build or u have questions, dm me on discord.

discord: kaneldev

stop asking for offsets and enjoy. :)

